snippet.title: You Are Vanguard
snippet.description:
EVE Vanguard is an MMOFPS set in the deep, persistent, far-future universe of New Eden. You are Vanguard – an elite mercenary fused with ancient technology, your immortal consciousness driving the tides of war. Deploy, gather resources, and dominate battles that ripple across New Eden’s player-driven conflicts. 

Wishlist EVE Vanguard on Steam today: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1872800/EVE_Vanguard/

Join the Discord - https://discord.gg/evevanguard 
EVE Vanguard forums - https://forums.eveonline.com/c/vanguard
Twitter - https://x.com/PlayEVEVanguard 
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/PlayEVEVanguard/ 
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/PlayEVEVanguard/ 
Twitch - https://www.twitch.tv/ccp
Youtube - @playevevanguard
